HEADWORD: Detecter
<hw>De*tect"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, detects or brings to light; one who finds out what another
attempts to conceal; a detector.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Detection</ent>⟦br⟧
